{"tid":151852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國製Pokemon「尿袋」有冒煙風險　日本呼籲停用並全面回收","createTime":"2017-03-11T08:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T11:40:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f5d6bd62ff124092bbd4b7ff86cb8357408d6ba","tid":151852,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"【中國製Pokemon「尿袋」有冒煙風險　日本呼籲停用並全面回收】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201703/fcc0a56b7dbe73de812e1c567fd3da01ddb50dab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201703%2Ffcc0a56b7dbe73de812e1c567fd3da01ddb50dab.jpg&h=839eca8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本The Pokemon Company於3月9日發出公告，自主回收兩款與日本NearbyDirect公司合作推出的移動電源（俗稱尿袋）。<br />\n<br />\n涉事移動電源型號為「ポケモン モバイルバッテリー　RAVPower 10050mAh　ピカチュウ」以及「ポケモン モバイルバッテリー　RAVPower 10050mAh　モンスターボール」兩款，機身分別印上比卡超或精靈球圖案，製造地為中國。<br />\n<br />\n據報告指，移動電源因製造過程出現問題，有可能在進行充電時出現異常發熱及冒煙情況，在2月份已有3宗同類情況發生，幸好未有受傷報告。The Pokemon Company呼籲用家立即停止使用，廠商已在日本各地的Pokemon Center及Pokemon Store設有回收站，也可經網上客戶服務查詢其它回收方法。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-11-2017/36500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-11-2017%2F36500&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUijQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0ccb9a88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-11-2017/36500</a><br />\n<br />\n#十萬伏特電能效應 #Pokemon #充電器 #尿袋 <br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise2&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUijQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5a42c1bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血主持育成計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUijQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=267a5240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise</a><br />\n<br />\n《熱血時報》 iOS，Android 同步抗共，歡迎下載：<br />\n<br />\niPhone<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/bpNcBn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbpNcBn&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUijQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5d4700d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/bpNcBn</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/IY4fHi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FIY4fHi&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUijQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=18a996cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/IY4fHi</a><br />\n--------------------<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想！<br />\nTill our dreams come true, we'll fight on."},{"pid":"30f1e5f221325a43bd73605192a5d9d1ab98e522","tid":151852,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:59:29.000Z","msg":"又中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db50c2facad9456dee20d049f7426b1a71df8105","tid":151852,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"尿袋容量：十萬伏特"},{"pid":"587285ef159203968c1555948b8becac60265ed9","tid":151852,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d98f874ed29d1ad6ded6e0059678e8bbfe286cb","tid":151852,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d0e291b97f01bf63998bcc706f43c906daf513","tid":151852,"uid":9722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"仲有人玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae300658463d2738344d7dafbf3cd8c778d4248a","tid":151852,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0